This map contains several things:

-HDR
-Color Correction
-Advanced geometry
-Displacement geometry
-Soundscape
-Warm colored lighting
-small ergonomic gungame style gameplay
-Env_sprite (realistic lights)
-Blend textures
-Custom Textures (pakratted in)
-40 player spawns
-Optimized with nodraw and func_detail (only things necessary)

All of these screenshots were taken in game without any editing. What you see is what you get

Please Enjoy the map!
